metadata.name: Welcome the New Year, let's start!
metadata.description:
It's always cold in this city  
but now is a really cold winter  
We welcome the New Year with fake happy faces,  
celebrating it close to paper fireplaces 

We imitate joy, follow the marketing plan,  
buy gifts and decorate our place.  
But deep inside it is hard to be fun  
because of the lack of embrace

We play a part in this celebration  
but in fact, it is empty to us.  
We're so tired of all bad sensations  
But in the paper fireplaces, there isn't the gas

But we stay hiding our pain  
and continue to play our part.  
Every year we play that game  
Welcome the New Year, let's start!
